title: UGREEN USB C to USB C Cable Fast Charger 60W PD Type C Power Data Lead Compatible with MacBook iPad Air 4 iPad Pro 2020…
html: UGREEN USB C to USB C Cable Fast Charger 60W PD Type C Power Data Lead Compatible with MacBook iPad Air 4 iPad Pro 2020…
description: PD 60W Power Delivery: UGREEN USB Type C to Type C Cable supports most fast charging protocols like USB Power Delivery, Qualcomm QC 4.0+/3.0 and Huawei FCP, and delivers 20V/3A (max), 15V/3A, 12V/3A, 9V/3A, 5V/3A when paired with 96W/87W/60W/45W/30W/18W power adapter. The 60W USB C to USB C Fast Charge Cable only takes 1.5h to fully recharge MacBook Air 13", 1h for Samsung Note 10. Ideal charger replacement cable for laptops/chromebooks/phones. 480Mbps Data Transfer: UGREEN USB C 2.0 to Thunderbolt 3 PD 60W Cable is not limited to a phone/laptop fast charger, and it also functions as a high-speed data transfer cable. The USB C to USB C Data Cable supports data transfer rates up to 480Mbps, 1G files will be transferred within 30s. It is convenient and easy to transfer the files, video, video clips, photos, movies from your Type C smartphones to laptop. The excellent choice to improve work efficiency and save time. High-Q USB C Cable: UGREEN 60W USB C to C Fast Charge Cable was produced by USB-IF certified manufacturer. Humanized design with the stronger and reinforced connector on both ends, 10000+ bending test to achieve a high bending strength and good toughness. Build-in Over-Current / Over-Temperature / Short-Circuit protection to protect your devices from damages.
